fill missing values¶

In [33]:
data['Preferred Foot'].fillna('Right',inplace=True)
data['International Reputation'].fillna(3,inplace=True)
data['Weak Foot'].fillna(3,inplace=True)
data['Weight'].fillna(66,inplace=True)
data['Height'].fillna("5'10",inplace=True)
data['Agility'].fillna(data['Agility'].mean(),inplace=True)
data['BallControl'].fillna(data['BallControl'].mean(),inplace=True)
data['ShotPower'].fillna(75,inplace=True)
data['Reactions'].fillna(80,inplace=True)
data['SprintSpeed'].fillna(72,inplace=True)
data['Acceleration'].fillna(data['Acceleration'].mean(),inplace=True)
data['LongPassing'].fillna(75,inplace=True)
data['HeadingAccuracy'].fillna(data['HeadingAccuracy'].mean(),inplace=True)
data['Jumping'].fillna(65,inplace=True)
data['Stamina'].fillna(data['Stamina'].mean(),inplace=True)
data['Strength'].fillna(data['Strength'].mean(),inplace=True)
data['Positioning'].fillna(65,inplace=True)
data['Penalties'].fillna(60,inplace=True)
data['StandingTackle'].fillna(67,inplace=True)
data['Loaned From'].fillna('None',inplace=True)
data['Wage'].fillna("225K",inplace=True)

FEATURE ENGINEERING¶

In [13]:
def defending(data):
    return int(round((data[['Marking','StandingTackle','SlidingTackle']].mean()).mean()))
def general(data):
    return int(round((data[['HeadingAccuracy','Dribbling','curve','ballcontrol']].mean()).mean()))
def mental(data):
    return int(round((data[['Aggression','Interceptions','positioning','Vision',
                            'Composure']].mean()).mean()))
def passing(data):
    return int(round((data[['Crossing','ShortPassing','LongPassing']].mean()).mean()))
def mobility(data):
    return int(round((data[['Acceleration','SprintSpeed','Agility','Reactions']].mean()).mean()))
def power(data):
    return int(round((data[['Balance','Jumping','Stamina','Strength']].mean).mean()))
def rating(data):
    return int(round((data[['Overall','Potential']].mean()).mean()))
def shooting(data):
    return int(round((data[['Finishing','Volleys','FKAccuracy','ShotPower','Longshots',
                           'Penalties']].mean()).mean()))
